1. *Živim* u Beogradu. (I live in Belgrade.)
2. *Živim* ovde već deset godina. (I have been living here for ten years.)
3. Ona *živi* sa decom. (She lives with children.)
4. Da li *živeš* sam? (Do you live alone?)
5. Mi *živimo* u istom gradu. (We live in the same city.)
6. Oni *žive* u Francuskoj. (They live in France.)
7. Ja *živim* u tom stanu već tri godine. (I have been living in that apartment for three years.)
8. Oni *žive* izvan grada. (They live outside the city.)